{
  "title": "Rabbit",
  "source": "stardewvalleywiki",
  "data": {
    "parse": {
      "title": "Rabbit",
      "pageid": 1896,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Rabbit\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 5px;\"><img alt=\"Rabbit.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/fd/Rabbit.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" />\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic;\">These are woolly rabbits! They shed precious wool every few days.  Lives in the coop.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Information\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Building\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Deluxe Coop.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/51/Deluxe_Coop.png/24px-Deluxe_Coop.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"28\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/5/51/Deluxe_Coop.png/36px-Deluxe_Coop.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/5/51/Deluxe_Coop.png/48px-Deluxe_Coop.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Deluxe Coop</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Purchase Price\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"8000 \"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />8,000g</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Produce\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png/24px-Rabbit%27s_Foot.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png/36px-Rabbit%27s_Foot.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Rabbit%27s_Foot\" title=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot\">Rabbit's Foot</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Wool.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Wool.png/24px-Wool.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Wool.png/36px-Wool.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/34/Wool.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p>The <b>Rabbit</b> is a farm <a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">animal</a> that lives in a <a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Deluxe Coop</a>. Rabbits can be purchased at <a href=\"/Marnie%27s_Ranch\" title=\"Marnie&#39;s Ranch\">Marnie's Ranch</a> for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"8000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />8,000g</span>. A rabbit cannot reproduce. A rabbit makes a soft sniffing sound when it is petted.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Produce\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Produce</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selling\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selling</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Produce\">Produce</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Rabbit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Produce\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>Main article: <a href=\"/Animals#Produce\" title=\"Animals\">Animals#Produce</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Rabbits who eat every day mature after 6 nights have passed. A mature and fed rabbit produces <a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a> every 4 days, which sells for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"340\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />340g</span>. They will drop it on their own so they do not need to be sheared. Once sufficient <a href=\"/Animals#Friendship\" title=\"Animals\">friendship</a> and happiness are reached, a rabbit may produce a <a href=\"/Rabbit%27s_Foot\" title=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot\">Rabbit's Foot</a> instead of wool, which sells for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"565\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />565g</span>.\n</p><p>Wool can be placed in a <a href=\"/Loom\" title=\"Loom\">Loom</a> to produce <a href=\"/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">Cloth</a>, which sells for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"470\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />470g</span>.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Sell Price\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Rabbit%27s_Foot.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Rabbit%27s_Foot\" title=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot\">Rabbit's Foot</a>\n</td>\n<td>Some say it's lucky.\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r146727\">.mw-parser-output .parent,.mw-parser-output .backimage,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent{position:relative;top:0;left:0}.mw-parser-output .backimage img,.mw-parser-output .foreimage img,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{display:block}.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{opacity:0.6}.mw-parser-output .foreimage{position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0}</style><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png/24px-Rabbit%27s_Foot.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png/36px-Rabbit%27s_Foot.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>565g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png/24px-Rabbit%27s_Foot.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png/36px-Rabbit%27s_Foot.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>706g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png/24px-Rabbit%27s_Foot.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png/36px-Rabbit%27s_Foot.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>847g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png/24px-Rabbit%27s_Foot.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png/36px-Rabbit%27s_Foot.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/c/ca/Rabbit%27s_Foot.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>1,130g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Wool.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Wool.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/34/Wool.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a>\n</td>\n<td>Soft, fluffy wool.\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Wool.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Wool.png/24px-Wool.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Wool.png/36px-Wool.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/34/Wool.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>340g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Wool.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Wool.png/24px-Wool.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Wool.png/36px-Wool.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/34/Wool.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>425g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Wool.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Wool.png/24px-Wool.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Wool.png/36px-Wool.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/34/Wool.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>510g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Wool.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Wool.png/24px-Wool.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/3/34/Wool.png/36px-Wool.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/3/34/Wool.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>680g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selling\">Selling</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Rabbit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selling\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Rabbits can be sold. The selling price is dependent on how many hearts the animal has (<span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"10400\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />10,400g</span> max).\n</p><p>To sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much the animal can be sold for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Rabbit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">Pigs</a> and rabbits are the only animals in the game for which both male and female animals are possible. However, rabbits are the only livestock animal that cannot reproduce.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Rabbit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The gender of animals is set by <samp>FarmAnimal::isMale</samp> in the game code. The only effect in-game is the pronoun used in some dialogs (<i>e.g.,</i> when <a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\">Marnie</a> says she'll \"send little [Name] to his/her new home\"); see <samp>PurchaseAnimalsMenu::marnieAnimalPurchaseMessage</samp>, <samp>FarmAnimal::getMoodMessage</samp>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">Animals</a> and Produce\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coop</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Chicken\" title=\"Chicken\">Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Dinosaur\" title=\"Dinosaur\">Dinosaur</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Dinosaur_Egg\" title=\"Dinosaur Egg\">Dinosaur Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Duck\" title=\"Duck\">Duck</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Feather\" title=\"Duck Feather\">Duck Feather</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Golden_Chicken\" title=\"Golden Chicken\">Golden Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a>)</sup> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Rabbit</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a> • <a href=\"/Rabbit%27s_Foot\" title=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot\">Rabbit's Foot</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Void_Chicken\" title=\"Void Chicken\">Void Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Void_Egg\" title=\"Void Egg\">Void Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cow\" title=\"Cow\">Cow</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Goat\" title=\"Goat\">Goat</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Sheep\" title=\"Sheep\">Sheep</a>  <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Ostrich\" title=\"Ostrich\">Ostrich</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">Pig</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Truffle\" title=\"Truffle\">Truffle</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Fish\" title=\"Fish\">Fish</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Roe\" title=\"Roe\">Roe</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Slime_Hutch\" title=\"Slime Hutch\">Slime Hutch</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Slimes\" title=\"Slimes\">Slimes</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Slime\" title=\"Slime\">Slime</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Ball\" title=\"Slime Ball\">Slime Ball</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Egg\" title=\"Slime Egg\">Slime Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Cat</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Dog</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Horse\" title=\"Animals\">Horse</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Additional_Pets\" title=\"Animals\">Turtle</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414014233\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nC