      "wikitext": "{{Infobox animal\n|image    = Rabbit.png\n|buyprice = 8000\n|building = {{Name|Deluxe Coop}}\n|produce  = {{Name|Rabbit's Foot}}{{Name|Wool}}\n}}\nThe '''Rabbit''' is a farm [[Animals|animal]] that lives in a [[Coop|Deluxe Coop]]. Rabbits can be purchased at [[Marnie's Ranch]] for {{Price|8000}}. A rabbit cannot reproduce. A rabbit makes a soft sniffing sound when it is petted.\n\n==Produce==\n{{main article|Animals#Produce}}\nRabbits who eat every day mature after 6 nights have passed. A mature and fed rabbit produces [[Wool]] every 4 days, which sells for {{Price|340}}. They will drop it on their own so they do not need to be sheared. Once sufficient [[Animals#Friendship|friendship]] and happiness are reached, a rabbit may produce a [[Rabbit's Foot]] instead of wool, which sells for {{Price|565}}.\n\nWool can be placed in a [[Loom]] to produce [[Cloth]], which sells for {{Price|470}}.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Sell Price\n|-\n|[[File:Rabbit's Foot.png]]\n|[[Rabbit's Foot]]\n|{{Description|Rabbit's Foot}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Rabbit's Foot|565|dsv=false}}\n|-\n|[[File:Wool.png]]\n|[[Wool]]\n|{{Description|Wool}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Wool|340|dsv=false}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==Selling==\nRabbits can be sold. The selling price is dependent on how many hearts the animal has ({{Price|10400}} max).\n\nTo sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much the animal can be sold for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n\n==Trivia==\n*[[Pig]]s and rabbits are the only animals in the game for which both male and female animals are possible. However, rabbits are the only livestock animal that cannot reproduce.<ref>The gender of animals is set by <samp>FarmAnimal::isMale</samp> in the game code. The only effect in-game is the pronoun used in some dialogs (''e.g.,'' when [[Marnie]] says she'll \"send little [Name] to his/her new home\"); see <samp>PurchaseAnimalsMenu::marnieAnimalPurchaseMessage</samp>, <samp>FarmAnimal::getMoodMessage</samp>.</ref>\n\n==References==\n<references />\n\n{{NavboxAnimals}}\n\n[[Category:Coop animals]]\n\n[[de:Hase]]\n[[es:Conejo]]\n[[fr:Lapin]]\n[[it:Coniglio]]\n[[ja:ウサギ]]\n[[ko:토끼]]\n[[hu:Nyúl]]\n[[pt:Coelho]]\n[[ru:Кролик]]\n[[tr:Tavşan]]\n[[zh:兔子]]"
